    <item>
      <title>沙特努力避免与也门胡塞武装再次爆发战争</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-26/saudi-arabia-strives-to-avoid-renewed-war-with-yemen-s-houthis</link>
      <description><![CDATA[沙特阿拉伯对邻国也门的局势越来越担忧，伊朗支持的胡塞武装加剧了与以色列的敌对行动，并威胁要攻击这个石油资源丰富的王国，因为以色列声称沙特正在对他们发动经济战。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-26/saudi-arabia-strives-to-avoid-renewed-war-with-yemen-s-houthis</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 26 Jul 2024 16:06:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>BancTrust 计划在选举后组织债券投资者前往委内瑞拉</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-26/banctrust-plans-bond-investor-trip-to-venezuela-after-election</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，投资银行 BancTrust &amp; Co. 正在组织持有委内瑞拉 600 亿美元违约债务的投资者前往委内瑞拉进行一次罕见的旅行。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-26/banctrust-plans-bond-investor-trip-to-venezuela-after-election</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 26 Jul 2024 15:54:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>白宫摩擦后特朗普向内塔尼亚胡致以热情问候</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-26/netanyahu-set-to-meet-trump-after-harris-calls-for-war-to-end</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周五，唐纳德·特朗普在海湖庄园给予了以色列总理本雅明·内塔尼亚胡他所希望的热烈欢迎，此前这位以色列人遭到了华盛顿总统候选人卡马拉·哈里斯的含蓄谴责。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-26/netanyahu-set-to-meet-trump-after-harris-calls-for-war-to-end</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 26 Jul 2024 15:33:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
